1
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:12,320
Xieyun converged here.

2
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:14,760
Solving this mystery

3
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:16,000
might

4
00:00:16,360 --> 00:00:18,240
lead us to a way to eliminate Xieyun.

5
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:41,600
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 9]

6
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,600
You're awake.

7
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:06,400
Earlier, your mind was damaged.

8
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,760
This herbal bath

9
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:09,560
will help you restore your energy
and calm your mind.

10
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,200
What...

11
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,360
What's wrong?

12
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:17,960
I'm fine.

13
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,200
Stay in a while longer.

14
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,360
I'll be right outside.

15
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:22,800
Hey!

16
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,960
I... I'm Mingling.

17
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:31,400
Mingling?

18
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,440
Since you're in the immortal realm,

19
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,360
you should have a proper immortal name.

20
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,000
Starting today,

21
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,080
you will be called Yaoyang.

22
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,400
Yaoyang.

23
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,200
Oh,

24
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:45,240
there's food prepared by the tub.

25
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,560
Remember to eat.

26
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,280
The starry sky here

27
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,600
is really beautiful.

28
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,840
This is the immortal realm.

29
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,000
If you want to see skies like this,

30
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,400
you can see them

31
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,000
every day here.

32
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,240
Immortal realm?

33
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,080
Are you an immortal?

34
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,560
I am Xiyin.

35
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,960
You cn call me Immortal Xiyin.

36
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,840
Don't just stand there.

37
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,160
Come have some tea.

38
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,640
There's no need to be so formal.

39
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:47,960
From now on,

40
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,760
this will be your home.

41
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,320
My home?

42
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,640
You want to keep me locked up here?

43
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,800
There is an evil entity

44
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,120
inside you.

45
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,120
If it isn't destroyed,

46
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:03,040
it'll slowly consume your mind

47
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,720
until it fully controls you.

48
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,320
Evil entity?

49
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:15,880
Earlier,

50
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,720
the immortal sect members
acted against you

51
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,600
out of necessity.

52
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,800
If this evil isn't removed,

53
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,480
it could bring catastrophe

54
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,440
to the Three Realms.

55
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,760
But

56
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,560
why?

57
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,840
You want to know

58
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,520
why this evil entered your body?

59
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:33,440
Yes.

60
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,440
I don't know.

61
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,080
Perhaps

62
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,600
it was simply fate.

63
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,960
I'll do my best to help you
get rid of the evil inside you.

64
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,760
Once you're back to normal,

65
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,400
I'll send you back.

66
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,320
Drink this calming tea.

67
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,160
Come with me later.

68
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:27,240
You'll stay in this room from now on.

69
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,720
I'll be right next door.

70
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,080
Starting tomorrow,

71
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,440
I'll teach you immortal arts
to suppress the evil.

72
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:35,160
Get some rest early tonight.

73
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,400
What...

74
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,840
What is this?

75
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,000
Then this mortal would...

76
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,320
We can't worry about that now.

77
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,240
Xieyun can't be destroyed.

78
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,320
It can only be sealed away.

79
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,120
Get in formation!

80
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,560
You three immortals,

81
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,040
I'm just

82
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,720
a fox demon with barely a hundred years
of cultivation.

83
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,560
Why make things difficult for me?

84
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,400
He only has a hundred years
of cultivation?

85
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,320
Capturing a minor demon

86
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,720
like him

87
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,120
won't earn much praise from our master.

88
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:18,240
He's full of lies!

89
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,400
I met him three hundred years ago,

90
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,680
and he told me the same thing then.

91
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,120
Something is better than nothing.

92
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,280
I'll take him!

93
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,680
I found him first.

94
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,160
I found him first!

95
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,880
So what if you did?

96
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,600
Enough arguing!

97
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:34,080
Go now.

98
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:37,200
The three of you gang up on one.

99
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,480
That's not fair!

100
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,400
Who are you, kid?

101
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,000
How dare you meddle
in our immortal sect's affairs?

102
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,240
I recognize him.

103
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,680
He's the fiend taken in

104
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,560
by Immortal Xiyin.

105
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,360
What's he doing here?

106
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,480
Must have sneaked out on his own.

107
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,360
Capturing him and bringing him back
to our master

108
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,040
would count as a major merit.

109
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,400
Fiendish aura.

110
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,920
Master.

111
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,760
He's the one

112
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:25,880
who injured us.

113
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:28,840
Just as I thought.

114
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,000
I sensed Xieyun's power

115
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,240
and rushed over.

116
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,480
Xiyin, what is going on?

117
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,680
Immortal Dehua, please calm down.

118
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,160
There's more to this situation.

119
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,640
I don't care about the details!

120
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,960
You allowed Xieyun
to injure my disciples.

121
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:41,960
I will

122
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,200
report this truthfully
to the Immortal Venerable.

123
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,800
I'll be leaving.

124
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:48,720
Now

125
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,960
Yang is in real trouble.

126
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:54,640
I know.

127
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,280
You hurt them accidentally

128
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,440
while trying to save that fox demon.

129
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,440
I'll ask you one thing.

130
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,400
Would you like me to be your master?

131
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,000
I'll take that as a yes.

132
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,040
Can you really

133
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,960
get rid of the evil inside me?

134
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,800
I'll do everything I can.

135
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,680
I'd like you

136
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,480
to be my master.

137
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,360
From this day on,

138
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,880
no matter what happens,

139
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,600
I will keep you safe.

140
00:08:59,740 --> 00:09:02,480
♪What is flickering?♪

141
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:05,220
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

142
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:11,220
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

143
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:14,100
♪What is falling?♪

144
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:17,340
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

145
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:22,780
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

146
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,300
♪When petals drift down♪

147
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,800
♪When the rain falls all around♪

148
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:29,500
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

149
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:31,360
♪Beyond the dunes♪

150
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:32,740
♪No end in sight♪

151
00:09:32,740 --> 00:09:35,740
♪I am like a mayfly♪

152
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:37,300
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

153
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,800
♪Nor will I run away♪

154
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:41,760
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

155
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:47,020
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

156
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:04,080
♪What is flickering?♪

157
00:10:04,300 --> 00:10:06,780
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

158
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:12,780
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

159
00:10:13,220 --> 00:10:16,020
♪What is falling?♪

160
00:10:16,140 --> 00:10:18,960
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

161
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:24,180
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

162
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:26,780
♪When petals drift down♪

163
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:28,280
♪When the rain falls all around♪

164
